1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 20=

4
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:54,000
She was the one you called

5
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:56,960
the kindest,

6
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:00,720
sweetest girl.

7
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,960
Wasn't she?

8
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:13,640
Yes.

9
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:20,680
Now I understand everything.

10
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,160
What do you understand?

11
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:32,880
I understand why you approached me.

12
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,040
Why you've treated me this way.

13
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,200
I understand it all.

14
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:44,720
Enough.

15
00:01:50,395 --> 00:01:57,275
♪There's no point in keeping this up♪

16
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,760
Enough?

17
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,920
You think shedding a few tears

18
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,040
is enough?

19
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,680
The same fire.

20
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,160
She died.

21
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,920
You lived.

22
00:02:17,735 --> 00:02:21,600
♪We've long been stuck on each other♪

23
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,720
Why?

24
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,920
Could I be the killer?

25
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,080
How do you know you're not?

26
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:34,595
♪Go find your own simple happiness♪

27
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,760
Fine.

28
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:38,775
♪Don't come and destroy me♪

29
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,160
Even if that fire was an accident,

30
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,360
what about Ye Xiaoduo's miserable life?

31
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,001
♪Why won't you leave?♪

32
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,320
That wasn't an accident.

33
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,040
All of this happened because of you.

34
00:02:53,641 --> 00:02:54,720
♪Did you ever hurt me?♪

35
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,680
Yes.

36
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,120
It was all me.

37
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,120
So you think

38
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:04,240
I'm the one who deserves to die,

39
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,240
right?

40
00:03:09,763 --> 00:03:15,183
♪Only seeing you fall♪

41
00:03:15,203 --> 00:03:19,213
♪The only way I'll truly be happy♪

42
00:03:22,023 --> 00:03:28,103
♪Someday I'll come see you
with my luggage♪

43
00:03:28,153 --> 00:03:33,353
♪Watching you cry all alone♪

44
00:03:33,363 --> 00:03:37,893
♪While I travel away with a smile♪

45
00:03:37,913 --> 00:03:41,863
♪Without a trace of emotion♪

46
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:45,720
Xiaomi.

47
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:48,000
You haven't come in
for a follow-up in a long time.

48
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,280
I'm worried about you.

49
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:51,880
You're at a critical stage
of recovering your memories.

50
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,040
You can't give up so easily.

51
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,800
Thank you, Dr. Chen.

52
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,480
But I've already decided to stop.

53
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,200
Xiaomi.

54
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,760
Trying to interfere with it like this

55
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,280
will only make you suffer more.

56
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:05,880
Let me help you, okay?

57
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,320
No.

58
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,840
I don't want to remember anymore.

59
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,880
I'm tired. I want to rest.

60
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,400
Where's Qin Yu?

61
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,880
Doesn't he want you
to get better either?

62
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,360
We're over.

63
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,920
Qin Yu isn't Ji Ran.

64
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,640
How did it go?

65
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,160
My star actor.

66
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,800
That heartwarming tea garden trip

67
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,920
must've brought you two
a lot closer, right?

68
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,480
She's emotionally unstable.

69
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,280
She's suffering.

70
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,480
Suffering?

71
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,840
Suffering is good.

72
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,400
Pain makes people cling.

73
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,400
The more she suffers,

74
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,040
the more she'll depend on you.

75
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,440
I'll make things even worse.

76
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,960
Make her suffer even more.

77
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,440
Hello, Xiaomi?

78
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,360
I...

79
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,360
I'm sorry.

80
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,720
I'm sorry.

81
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,680
Why are you apologizing?

82
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,960
Chen Yue?

83
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:03,440
Why do you have Xiaomi's phone?

84
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,560
Qin Yu,

85
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,360
you're really something.

86
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,920
Apologizing to a murderer?

87
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,360
Hello?

88
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,400
Hello?

89
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,000
Xiaomi.

90
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,440
The next stage of treatment
will be extremely painful.

91
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,760
We'll use the harshest method possible

92
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,400
to uncover the memories
buried deep inside you.

93
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,000
Are you ready?

94
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,200
Yes.

95
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,520
Qin Yu isn't Ji Ran.

96
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,160
What?

97
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,200
The Ji Ran in front of you
isn't the real Ji Ran.

98
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,600
The real Ji Ran died long ago.

99
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,760
Because of you, Qiao Xiaomi,

100
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,400
he died in that fire three years ago.

101
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,360
That's impossible.

102
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,560
What are you talking about?

103
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,960
Do you think I'm joking with you?

104
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,200
Who are you?

105
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,720
I'm Ji Ran's elder brother.

106
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,760
Qiao Xiaomi,

107
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,960
you have no right to forget the past.

108
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,280
And even less right to forget
the boy who loved you deeply.

109
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,920
and died in that fire for you.

110
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,800
Do you want to know
what happened back then?

111
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,240
Do you want to know who he is?

112
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,440
Then stop running from it.

113
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,760
Xiaomi.

114
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,440
Right now,

115
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,680
you're the only one
who can find the truth.

116
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,480
Come with me.

117
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,880
I'll show you the truth.

118
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,960
Ji Ran,

119
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,960
soon,

120
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:17,000
everything will come to light.

121
00:08:26,468 --> 00:08:28,480
(Psychological Intervention)

122
00:08:30,851 --> 00:08:31,520
(Feb. 15, 2023. A stranger
showed up in my memories.)

123
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,560
(Mar. 26, 2024. Easel in my memory.)
Dad,

124
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,720
I really can't paint anymore.

125
00:08:34,906 --> 00:08:35,280
(Jul. 7, 2022. A girl was in my dream.)

126
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,200
(Jul. 7, 2022. A girl was in my dream.)
Don't be afraid.

127
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:37,720
Take my hand.

128
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,040
I'll take you somewhere safe.

129
00:08:39,160 --> 00:08:40,685
(Aug. 31, 2022. Same fire dream again.)

130
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,960
Xiaomi.

131
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,920
Calm down.

132
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:48,360
(Dec. 3, 2023. Hospital. A woman. Mom?)
The body is its own universe.

133
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,920
Its meridians are like the stars.

134
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,560
(Ye Xiaoduo. Fire. Jealousy.)
This isn't trash.

135
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:56,000
My mom stitched it
for me herself.

136
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,960
Didn't your mom
ever make anything for you?

137
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,560
So you're jealous?

138
00:08:59,666 --> 00:09:00,520
(Qin Yu. Fiancé?)

139
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,640
(Qin Yu. A liar?)
Because he's a liar.

140
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,240
He said he could paint.

141
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,160
He said

142
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,240
he only loved you.

143
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:10,240
Too bad. It was all a lie.

144
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,600
Xiaomi.

145
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,720
Do you remember the fire now?

146
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,000
Xiaomi.

147
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,120
I'm Ji Ran.

148
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,400
Tell me.

149
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,800
Why did you do this to me?

150
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,560
Why were you okay?

151
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:34,200
Why did Ji Ran die?

152
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,560
How did the fire start?

153
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,640
Answer me.

154
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,600
Xiaoduo!

155
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,360
Xiaomi!

156
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,560
Xiaomi, you're in there, aren't you?

157
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:01,560
Xiaomi!

158
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,320
Xiaomi, are you in there?

159
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,160
Xiaomi!

160
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,080
Don't be scared!

161
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,360
I'm right outside, Xiaomi!

162
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,640
There's

163
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,000
someone else inside!

164
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,280
Help them.

165
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,400
Help them.

166
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:28,360
Help them.

167
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,120
Wait for me.

168
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,240
Xiaomi!

169
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:09,640
Xiaomi.

170
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,200
I'm sorry I'm late.

171
00:12:01,034 --> 00:12:03,104
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

172
00:12:03,104 --> 00:12:06,524
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

173
00:12:08,124 --> 00:12:10,014
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

174
00:12:10,014 --> 00:12:14,004
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

175
00:12:15,244 --> 00:12:17,104
♪Let me go, set me free♪

176
00:12:17,104 --> 00:12:21,144
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

177
00:12:21,684 --> 00:12:27,094
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

178
00:12:28,444 --> 00:12:30,584
♪The freedom you gave me♪

179
00:12:30,584 --> 00:12:34,224
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

180
00:12:35,484 --> 00:12:37,754
♪Love can barely move forward♪

181
00:12:37,754 --> 00:12:41,534
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

182
00:12:42,634 --> 00:12:44,874
♪The closeness I long for♪

183
00:12:44,874 --> 00:12:49,264
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

184
00:12:49,674 --> 00:12:51,494
♪I don't want to break free♪

185
00:12:51,494 --> 00:12:56,864
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
